description: This talk introduces AOTInductor, an Ahead-Of-Time version of TorchInductor. AOTInductor enables the compilation of exported models into shared libraries, offering a seamless and high-performance deployment solution for PyTorch models in non-Python environments. By leveraging torch.export, AOTInductor ensures a streamlined workflow for efficient PyTorch model deployment.
title: Lightning Talk: AOTInductor: Ahead-of-Time Compilation for PT2 Exported Models
